# Hardware Firmware (Future Release)

This directory is reserved for ESP32/Arduino C++ embedded source files[cite: 1]. 

The system currently runs on a robust standalone **Python Simulation and Streamlit Web Interface** located in the `python_simulation/` directory, which models real-time appliance usage metrics without physical hardware constraints[cite: 1]. 

*Note: Embedded firmware code for physical deployment will be pushed here in Phase 2[cite: 1].*